OL,7,FThere are fresh warnings about the
OL,8,Frisks posed by overhead electric
OL,9,Fcables on the railways, with Transport
OL,10,Ffor Wales (TfW) warning that contact
OL,11,Fwith the equipment can be "fatal nine
OL,12,Ftimes out of ten."
OL,14,FFigures from TfW reveal there were
OL,15,F1,000 incidents of trespass and anti-
OL,16,Fsocial behaviour on the core valley
OL,17,Flines in the last two years, with 73%
OL,18,Fof incidents involving people aged
OL,19,Funder 17.
