OL,7,FThe ongoing project to electrify the
OL,8,Fline means the risks of trespass don't
OL,9,Fjust come from the trains themselves.
OL,11,FPaul Lawrence, a train driver with
OL,12,FTfW, described an incident where a 14-
OL,13,Fyear-old boy had a near-miss ` and was
OL,14,Ffortunate the power wasn't turned on.
OL,16,F"My incident happened at Porth railway
OL,17,Fstation," Paul said.
