OL,7,F"In this situation the young boy did
OL,8,Fclimb the overhead line equipment, he
OL,9,Fclimbed up the gantry post which
OL,10,Fsupports the lines, and he did try to
OL,11,Ftouch them unfortunately.
OL,13,F"Luckily for us the lines were new on
OL,14,Fthe valleys and they hadn't been
OL,15,Fenergised yet.
OL,17,F"Fortunately he was OK after the
OL,18,Fincident, we managed to get him on the
OL,19,Ftrain and the British Transport Police
OL,20,Fcame and escorted him off the railway."
