OL,7,FThe overhead cables carry 25,000 volts
OL,8,Fof electricity.
OL,10,FLois Park, from TfW, says simply
OL,11,Fcoming too close to the equipment
OL,12,F(within 2.75 metres) could prove
OL,13,Fdeadly.
OL,15,F"The shock can be fatal nine times out
OL,16,Fof ten," she said.
OL,18,F"And the shock that you receive can be
OL,19,Fhot enough to ignite the victim's
OL,20,Fclothes and the victim themselves.
