OL,7,F"So it's a really dangerous risk that
OL,8,Fpeople are taking if they go beyond
OL,9,Fthat railway boundary."
OL,11,FThe traditional risks posed by
OL,12,Fstraying onto the railway tracks
OL,13,Fcontinue to apply.
OL,15,FCCTV from around Wales shows near-
OL,16,Fmisses featuring trespassers, with
OL,17,Fyoungsters sometimes deliberately
OL,18,Fjumping out of the way as a speeding
OL,19,Ftrain approaches.
