OL,7,FIt's something driver Rachel Walters
OL,8,Fhas experienced up close.
OL,10,FBy the time she saw two boys trying to
OL,11,Fclimb off the tracks at Energlyn and
OL,12,FChurchill Park Station in Caerphilly,
OL,13,Fit was too late to stop her train.
OL,15,F"I slammed the brake into emergency, I
OL,16,Fdidn't think I was going to stop in
OL,17,Ftime," Rachel remembers.
OL,19,F"But thankfully the boys managed to
OL,20,Fmove out of the way in time. It has
OL,21,Fstayed with me.
