OL,7,F"Every time I go through Energlyn I
OL,8,Fthink of that incident."
OL,10,FIncidents of trespass were actually
OL,11,Fdown over the last year ` by 38%. But
OL,12,Fcases of anti-social behaviour ` like
OL,13,Fthrowing stones at trains ` are up by
OL,14,F28%, with young people
OL,15,Fdisproportionately represented in both
OL,16,Fgroups.
OL,18,FFor those following the rules, train
OL,19,Ftravel has never been safer.
